{title: If You Can Walk Away}
{artist: Jean Shepard}
{composer: Written by Gertrude Cox and Jack Rhodes}

[C]If you can walk away from me and [F]all my love for [C]you
If you can turn your back upon the [D7]happiness we [G7]knew
[C]I won't even say goodbye I [F]understand we're [C]through
